This is a 2048 game written in C  (standard C99)
 with a little clean interface for shell.
Move with the arrows to get a 2048 box (or more).
It looks like this:

    ┌────┬────┬────┬────┐ Moves:    89
    │   4│   8│  64│ 128│
    ├────┼────┼────┼────┤
    │    │    │  16│   8│
    ├────┼────┼────┼────┤
    │    │    │   4│   2│
    ├────┼────┼────┼────┤
    │   4│    │    │   2│
    └────┴────┴────┴────┘

Hope you enjoy it :D
